config.script:
logger = system.util.getLogger('splitDTReason')
	queryPath = 'app/DT/splitDTReasonForEvent'
	stateEventID = self.view.params.RowData.EventID
	userName = self.session.custom.UserName
	
	split1Duration = self.parent.getChild("Split1Duration/NumericEntryField").props.value
	split1Notes = self.parent.getChild("Split1Notes/TextArea").props.text
	split1ReasonID = self.view.custom.Split1Reason
	split1SubReasonID = -1
	
	if self.parent.getChild("Split1SubReason/Dropdown").props.enabled:
		split1SubReasonID = self.view.custom.Split1Reason
		
	
	split2Duration =self.parent.getChild("Split2Duration/NumericEntryField").props.value
	split2Notes = self.parent.getChild("Split2Notes/TextArea").props.text
	split2ReasonID = self.view.custom.Split2Reason
	split2SubReasonID = -1
	
	if self.parent.getChild("Split2SubReason/Dropdown").props.enabled:
		split2SubReasonID = self.view.custom.Split2SubReason
		
	split1FinalID = split1ReasonID
	if split1SubReasonID is not -1:
		split1FinalID = split1SubReasonID
	
	split2FinalID = split2ReasonID
	if split2ReasonID is not -1:
		split2FinalID = split2ReasonID
	
	params = {
	    'stateEventID': stateEventID,
	    'userName': userName,
	    'split1Duration': split1Duration,
	    'split1ReasonID': split1FinalID,
	    'split1Notes': split1Notes,
	    'split2Duration': split2Duration,
	    'split2ReasonID': split2FinalID,
	    'split2Notes': split2Notes
	}
	system.perspective.print(params)
	
	
	try:
		if self.view.custom.Success:
			#system.db.runNamedQuery(queryPath, params)
			mes.downtime.sp.splitDTReasonsForEvent(stateEventID, 
				split1Duration,split1FinalID, split1Notes, 
				split2Duration, split2FinalID, split2Notes,userName)
		else:
			valueErrorMsg = "The split number can't be larger than the original event"
			raise ValueError(valueErrorMsg)
			gpa.frontEnd.localUI.throwError(valueErrorMsg)
	except Exception as e:
		gpa.frontEnd.localUI.throwError(str(e))
	else:
		system.perspective.closePopup('downtimePopup')
		system.perspective.sendMessage('changeDTEvent')
		gpa.frontEnd.localUI.throwSuccess('Split event')
